comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T20:58:17.040Z",codex-relationship-backfill-20260721,"Duplicate check 2026-07-21: searched all statuses for GH-634,global install executable missing,manifest_missing,and bundle-integrity reinstall. Closed pm-wfvq and pm-pz7xtx own torn-generation diagnosis,but neither covers npm publication removing the executable after a reported successful install; this item records the distinct installer atomicity failure."
